Find huge armor shop on DL2.  95% usual crap, but snag robe (saving
for later), displacement cloak, speed boots.  Wander into mines (also
from DL2).  Dog dies immediately somewhere in darkness.  No problem;
not AC8 any more, fast and AC3 instead, soldier on carefully, kill
gnomes and dwarves, collect daggers.  Arrive at grotto Minetown.  Make
kitten friend, speed teach hunting.  Test random wand; is polymorph.
Still in Minetown, XL8, kitty 72HP maxed, decide to revisit main
dungeon before doing mines in earnest.  Back to huge shop to make
better armor.  Forget what shopkeep does when goods are polymorphed.
Adopt wait and see attitude.  Pile couple dozen items in row, zap.
Kalecik is enraged!  Zaps twice!  Examine self, no smoking holes.  Oh,
am wearing cloak!  More zaps!  More misses!  Move into line with keep,
now, my turn to zap.  Kalecik the red naga hatchling bites!

No taming scroll handy, so enjoy snack of red naga hatchling sashimi.
